1. *Oduvek* je bio zaljubljen u nju. (He has always been in love with her.)
2. On se *oduvek* brinuo za svoju porodicu. (He has always taken care of his family.)
3. Ona je *oduvek* znala da će uspeti. (She has always known she would succeed.)
4. *Oduvek* je bio čovek velikog srca. (He has always been a man of great heart.)
5. *Oduvek* je želela da uči. (She has always wanted to learn.)